channel.title: New activate link
channel.description: When I went to register my account, my computer froze and closed the web browser, and I have lost the link to activate the MoparScape page, I went to try it again and it said you're server has Error: This server has already been posted, but not yet approved, have some patience!. But I do not believe it'll go unless I activate it from my VPS. Help please?

item.title: New activate link
item.dc:creator: @Tom Tom
item.description:
@Tom wrote:

Hey,

If your server isn’t activated, or checked within 24 hours it should be automatically deleted allowing you to repost it again, except complete the registration this time. In the mean time just ensure there is no way you can get the information, whether it be by clicking on “My server” and such.

If you’re unable to redo it 24 hours from now please shoot me a PM.
